    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. What about hair specifically? I have some clients who might have different textures or styles, like curly or coily hair, or maybe they prefer wearing head coverings for religious reasons. How should they approach hair and headwear to make sure they still come across as high-level and authoritative in those meetings?",
