    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. one thing I've heard from some people in the industry is that \"natural\" looks or more ethnic styles can sometimes be seen as less \"serious\" or \"polished\" in very old-school corporate settings. do you think there's any truth to that? like, is it better to lean towards more traditional, smoother looks to avoid any distractions in the boardroom?",
